ed="T" n="0889b23"/><persName key="A013839">釋僧達</persName>，姓王氏，<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName>人也。稚齒英奇，不參<lb
ed="T" n="0889b24"/>戲弄，於龜山<placeName key="PL000000013294">妙喜道場</placeName>出俗。<placeName key="PL000000013294">其寺</placeName><date key="j19045331909604" notAfter-iso="+0516-03-20" notBefore-iso="+0502-05-02">南梁</date>初<lb
ed="T" n="0889b25"/>建。後樂遊方，見<persName key="A000237">黃梅忍禪師</persName>，若枯苗得雨，<lb
ed="T" n="0889b26"/>隨順修禪，罔有休懈。遇<persName key="A009251">印宗禪師</persName>，重磨心<lb
ed="T" n="0889b27"/>鑑。<placeName key="PL000000025908">光州</placeName>見<persName key="A008876">道岸律師</persName>，更勵律儀。四眾<ptr type="glossary" target="#g98"/>依歸，<lb
ed="T" n="0889b28"/>如水宗海。<date key="j19617861961814" notAfter-iso="+0659-03-01" notBefore-iso="+0659-02-01">開元七年</date>示疾而終，春秋八十<lb
ed="T" n="0889b29"/>二云。</p>
